data.description:
Situated in the highly sought-after Old Mill Basin, this residence offers the best of both worlds. Enjoy a serene and friendly neighborhood atmosphere in this 1 Family/3 Bedroom colonial. The well-appointed kitchen, spacious living room, and dining area make it perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. With 1.5 baths and the added bonus of a semi-finished basement, this home offers versatility for storage or potential extra living space. Go outside and unwind in the serenity of your private backyard, providing an oasis for relaxation and outdoor activities.
Conveniently located near transportation hubs and a variety of shopping options, this delightful neighborhood ensures easy access to everything you need for a comfortable lifestyle. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to call Old Mill Basin your home.
